# Beihang data project

## Environment
* python2 >= 2.7.3
* python-opencv
    * Install opencv in ubuntu ```sudo apt-get install libopencv```
    * Install opencv in Mac OS X ```brew install opencv```

## Dataset

[google drive](https://drive.google.com/open?id=0BwSoUv9YA-zzXzBtVmExUlRsNTA)

## How to mark
1. The order :
    * Head -> spine -> left hand -> right hand -> left leg -> right leg

2. Keyboard
    * N : Next picture (You have to mark 16 points before going to next image)
    * X : If this point is invisible


